{"tid":1653062,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"銀髮族仲係警總 灣仔金鐘上班族12.30去聲援","createTime":"2019-10-14T02:26:46.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-14T05:33:43.000Z","uid":61690,"like":77,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":51,"replies":[{"pid":"9c7b3ad70ade491a949d7189d2fe5d15f461772d","tid":1653062,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:26:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/nAenAu0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FnAenAu0.jpg&h=8e313900&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n銀髮族已經差唔多留守係狗屋48小時，好多都好大年齡，坐係度就訓著，又落雨，一定好唔舒服，但佢地都堅持，我行過好心up<br />\n<br />\n行過覺得好感動，但見唔到有post講佢地既行動，我地作為同路人，我想灣仔金鐘上班族中午1230-1300 去條天橋度叫口號聲援佢地<br />\n<br />\n佢地已經守左兩日 銀髮族並不孤單<br />\n<br />\n光復香港 時代革命"},{"pid":"015bef58ca490deee07729670e00e0e540c8e201","tid":1653062,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:27:12.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"b0122ce1a789798652d81955527d5a6557d567e4","tid":1653062,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:27:35.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cf482fd8ff19362748322b92f35020a805f3f472","tid":1653062,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:27:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"275010f05737413e96ba728d563a28b92b1a969d","tid":1653062,"uid":61690,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:28:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f3a5ec5db82b1e636634d897e24980f41b241dbb","tid":1653062,"uid":32932,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:28:38.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ce75705c993af055a0904affcdc8d89d9a09ace5","tid":1653062,"uid":181747,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:28:45.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"8df2fe875768fe24076cbf734480d309a21c900f","tid":1653062,"uid":225192,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-14T02:28:59.000Z","msg":"幫推 放工再過海"},{"pid":"34a4619d9b23b657e82b2e98e608a4fdd32adaa2","tid":165306